# Web Scraping Automation (UiPath)

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates **web data extraction** using UiPath.  
It scrapes product details from a website and stores them in Excel.

## ⚙️ Workflow Steps
1. Open target website.
2. Scrape product listings (name, price, URL).
3. Save extracted data to Excel.
4. Generate daily report.

## 📊 Example Output
| Product Name   | Price  | URL                         |
|----------------|--------|-----------------------------|
| Laptop Model A | 55,000 | https://example.com/product |
| Laptop Model B | 62,000 | https://example.com/product |

## 🚀 Key Learning
- Data Scraping Wizard
- Handling dynamic selectors
- Excel output automation
